style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">結論是安心武力升級，班真紅笑9我哋，班真心反對暴力既愚民升唔升級武力都會鬧</span></span>"},{"pid":"6772d863f03f18e2caa3e6f3862225f3572a13bd","tid":1553890,"uid":103230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T18:34:54.000Z","msg":"不過我勸大家咪嘥時間同五毛理論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為人地根本唔係想同你理論<br />\n佢只係做緊抹黑工作<br />\n會不斷轉移話題<br />\n<br />\n你駁左abc佢講d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}